            }
          ],
          "type": "H4"
        },
        {
          "id": "7ab7d05b4b7d_30",
          "href": null,
          "name": "6bbe",
          "text": "I believe we can live partially into the answer to this questions by charting pathways based on constant feedback generated by asking ourselves the following guiding questions. They might inform a deeper understanding of how to participate appropriately in these complex systems:",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "7ab7d05b4b7d_31",
          "href": null,
          "name": "1e4b",
          "text": "Who are the participants in the systems and what is meaningful to them?",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
